<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#f1ebd9]">
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 md:items-center">
        <div class="relative flex-1 reveal">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589187151003-0dd55769239b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Authentic Kerala Spices and Food" class="rounded-[24px] shadow-xl w-full object-cover" />
            <div class="absolute -bottom-5 right-4 md:right-10 bg-[#dca43b] text-[#1e4a30] p-4 md:py-4 md:px-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg text-center">
                <span class="block text-lg md:text-xl tracking-widest font-bold">★★★★★</span>
                <span class="font-semibold text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Rated 5 Stars</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 reveal delay-1 mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <span class="inline-block text-[#c75438] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-[0.85rem] mb-3">Our Heritage</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-[2.8rem] font-heading text-[#1e4a30] leading-tight mb-6">A Symphony of Spices in Hamilton</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed">At Mallu's Corner, we don't just serve food; we serve a piece of our home. Every dish is a tribute to the rich culinary legacy of Kerala, meticulously prepared with hand-picked spices and traditional techniques.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed">Whether you're craving authentic South Indian delicacies, perfectly spiced Chinese fusion, or aromatic Arabic dishes, our masterful chefs ensure an unforgettable experience.</p>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-4 font-medium text-[#1e4a30] text-[1.05rem]">
                    <span class="bg-[#faf8f5] w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full shadow-sm text-lg">🌿</span> Authentic Kerala Spices
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-4 font-medium text-[#1e4a30] text-[1.05rem]">
                    <span class="bg-[#faf8f5] w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full shadow-sm text-lg">🌶️</span> Indo-Chinese Fusion
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-4 font-medium text-[#1e4a30] text-[1.05rem]">
                    <span class="bg-[#faf8f5] w-11 h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full shadow-sm text-lg">👨‍🍳</span> Expert Regional Chefs
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
